00:05:29.839 --> 00:05:31.000
My little Chenyu.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.399
Come quickly.

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:34.839
Grandma will sing you a song.

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:40.879
Just sleep.

00:05:41.319 --> 00:05:44.720
My dear little one.

00:05:45.279 --> 00:05:48.240
