keep stepping on you like this?

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:49.079
Yansheng.

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:50.120
Look at me.

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.279
Trust me.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.439
